c: 53
v: 32
t: "Isaan sun warra dogoggora xixiqqoo malee dilii gugurdoofi sagaagalummaa irraa fagaataniidhaDhugumatti, Gooftaan kee araaramni Isaa bal’aadhaInni yeroo dachii irraa isin uumeefi yeroo isin garaa haadha keessanii keessatti ulfa taatanii jirtan akkaan isin beekaLubbuu keessan hin qulqulleessinaaInni nama (Isa) sodaatu akkaan beekaadha"